necessary implementations:
bleed - deal 3 damage at the end of turn (per stack)
burn - deal 5% of current hp per turn (per stack)


special functionalities:
placebo pills
base attack damage * 3 and 50% lifesteal for 4 turns
drake hunter
deal base attack damage * 5, execute enemies with < 50 hp
burn it all
deal base attack damage * 3 and apply 5 burn to enemy
experimental gadget
for each item in your inventory, deal base damage * 2
muay thai counter
whatever incoming damge is nullified and reflected
brutal tackle
deal current hp as damage
serrated slash
deal base damage 2x and apply 10 bleed
assassination
deal damage equal to base damage * (move radius / 100)
budget necromancy
deal damage = to the sum of base damage of every zombie you've fought this game


